title: Randy Weston Interview - July 2018
description:
Randy Weston interview at the Nice Jazz Festival 2018 by Alain Karsenty for Riviera Jazz Club.
This took place a few weeks before Randy passed away on September. It was a great honor meeting such an outstanding artist and above all great human personality that was a living legend of jazz music, with such an insight to share with us.

Many thanks to Frederica Randrianome for the precious advices.
